pair of collapsed residential buildings. One of the buildings, a four-story
brownstone apartment building, collapsed Tuesday night on a quiet street in
Brooklyn, bringing down much of an adjacent three-story building. The roof of
the first building fell without breaking, making it more difficult for rescue
workers to look for survivors underneath.
